### Roles

- Product Owner : Boss of the vision of the final product, usually the customer
- Scrum Master : Organisator. Veil to the smart attribution of tasks and protect workers from perturbations. Know as Sherped dog or Firewall too, he is the guarantor of the respect of the general process.
  -- Note : This 2 roles are not project manager. In SCRUM, their is no need of project manager
- Dev Team
